これから始まる季節に挨拶
Greeting the season that's about to begin,

130
00:15:23,541 --> 00:15:28,841
これから始める my life, my life, my life!
starting from now, my life, my life, my life!

131
00:15:57,541 --> 00:16:02,841
気がついたときには 生まれてた
By the time I realized it, I was born.

132
00:16:02,841 --> 00:16:07,541
なぜだろう さあね
Why is that? Who knows.

133
00:16:07,541 --> 00:16:12,541
意識がもう育ちつつあるよ
