140
00:16:35,141 --> 00:16:37,541
本気でワンチャンある！？
...is there seriously a chance!?

141
00:16:37,541 --> 00:16:42,141
今より素敵な未来があるから
Because there is a brighter future than now,

142
00:16:42,141 --> 00:16:47,341
今より素敵に my life, my life, my life!
more beautifully than now, my life, my life, my life!

143
00:16:53,341 --> 00:16:57,541
はい！というわけで始まりました！
Yes! And so it has begun!

144
00:16:57,541 --> 00:17:01,541
2026桃鈴ねね誕生日、イェーイ！
2026 Momosuzu Nene's Birthday, yay!

145
