Right now, my egosearch screen is lagging a bit,

151
00:17:18,541 --> 00:17:20,841
こっちでツイートしてくれたらめっちゃ嬉しいです！
so I'd be super happy if you could tweet with this!

152
00:17:20,841 --> 00:17:23,141
よろしくお願いします！
Thank you!

153
00:17:23,141 --> 00:17:25,341
今日はね、超重大告知があるんで
Today, we have a super major announcement,

154
00:17:25,341 --> 00:17:29,341
最後まで楽しんでいってください！
so please enjoy until the very end!

155
00:17:29,341 --> 00:17:32,341
